data.description: Welcome home to the this gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in the heart of Cedar Creek in Snyder! House features new vinyl flooring throughout, a wet bar, an office that could be used as a 4th bedroom, formal dining, plus a breakfast area off of the kitchen. The backyard has a new privacy fence, storage building and a great sunroom for your next gathering! Lots of built-in storage, a sequestered master suite with dual sinks and walk-in closets! Come make this your new home for the new year!
